  "cooking_instructions": [
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Preheat the oven to 220°C/ 200°C (fan)/ Gas 7</p><p>Line a <strong>medium</strong> <strong>deep baking tray</strong> or<strong> oven-proof dish</strong> with <strong>baking paper </strong>and add 3 tbsp<span class=\"text-danger\"> [6 tbsp] </span><strong>vegetable oil</strong></p><p>Tip: Cooking for 4? Use a larger deep tray or dish!</p><p>Add the <strong>Cumberland sausages</strong> and put the tray on the top shelf of the oven for an initial 10 min or until the sausages are starting to brown slightly and the oil is hot</p>",
      "order": 1,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-1-1618925777756-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-1-1618925777756-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-1-1618925777756-x700.jpg",
            "width": 700
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-1-1618925777756-x1000.jpg",
            "width": 1000
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-1-1618925777756-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, strip the<strong> thyme leaves</strong> from their stalks and chop the leaves finely</p><p>Combine the<strong> egg<span class=\"text-danger\">[s]</span></strong> with 35g<span class=\"text-danger\"> [70g] </span><strong>plain flour</strong> and 50ml <span class=\"text-danger\">[100ml] </span><strong>milk</strong> and whisk in<strong> half</strong> the <strong>chopped thyme </strong>(save the rest for later!)</p><p>Season with a pinch of<strong> salt</strong> – this is your<strong> herby batter</strong></p><p>Put the <strong>herby batter</strong> in the fridge to rest</p>",
      "order": 2,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-2-1618925812113-x200.jpg",
