            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-3-1618925839344-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Remove the sausage tray from the oven and carefully pour the<strong> herby batter</strong> into it</p><p>Return the tray to the oven for 20-25 min or until the sausages are cooked through and the <strong>Yorkshire pudding</strong> has puffed up</p><p>Tip: Don't peek! Opening the oven might make your giant Yorkie collapse!</p><p>Meanwhile, dissolve the<strong> chicken stock mix </strong>and <strong>Marmite </strong>in<strong> </strong>250ml<span class=\"text-danger\"> [450ml]</span> <strong>boiled water</strong></p>",
      "order": 4,
